          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The symmetry about 90-degree would suggest",
                "that the reaction proceeds through states of definity",
                "parity in N-13. By contrast, at 22.8-MeV, in the energy",
                "region between two of the resonances, the asymmetry",
                "of the angular distribution indicates that two levels",
                "of opposite parity may be interfering with one another."
              ]
            }
          ],
